title: Karnis – Taste the difference.
snippet: AUTHENTIC Mediterranean Flavors... With more than 50 years of family tradition, Karnis brings you fresh original Hummus and Mediterranean salads.

title: Dips – Karnis
snippet: Original Hummus Our Hummus is velvety smooth, creamy in texture and incredibly authentic in taste. More than just a dip, Karnis Hummus is our traditional creation!

title: F.A.Qs – Karnis
snippet: Are Karnis Hummus and More products Kosher? Yes, we believe that everyone deserves to enjoy our delicious salads and dips therefore we are certified by OK Kosher Certification, one of the major kosher certification agencies. Look for the Logo. Are Karnis Hummus & More products Gluten-Free?

title: About – Karnis
snippet: Karnis Hummus Factory is the first of its kind in Florida, promising the superlative quality hummus and a rich line of associated products. Inside the factory, the latest tools, technologies and practices are being continually adopted to harness the well-kept secrets of Mediterranean recipes.
